OL,3,CSainsbury's to hire 20,000 staff for
OL,4,CChristmas season
OL,6,FSainsbury's will be hiring 20,000 more
OL,7,Fshop workers, warehouse staff and
OL,8,Fdrivers for the Christmas period as
OL,9,Fthe retailer prepares for festive
OL,10,Fshoppers.
OL,12,FApplications have opened for seasonal
OL,13,Fstaff, who will be employed for up to
OL,14,Fthree months during its busiest time
OL,15,Fof year.
OL,17,FThe UK-wide roles will include 18,000
OL,18,Fat Sainsbury's and 2,000 at Argos.
