OL,3,CSainsbury's to hire 20,000 staff for
OL,4,CChristmas season
OL,6,FThe positions range from shop workers,
OL,7,Fincluding restocking shelves, staff in
OL,8,Fwarehouses to pick and prepare stock,
OL,9,Fand drivers for home deliveries.
OL,11,FStaff will be employed on fixed-term
OL,12,Fcontracts ranging from three weeks to
OL,13,Fthree months.
OL,15,FHourly pay for in-store and warehouse
OL,16,Femployees ranges from #12 to #13.50,
OL,17,Fdepending on the location and the
OL,18,Frole, and between #13 and #14.65 for
OL,19,Fdrivers.
