OL,3,CSainsbury's to hire 20,000 staff for
OL,4,CChristmas season
OL,6,FWorkers are also offered free food
OL,7,Fduring shifts and a 10% discount
OL,8,Facross stores, rising to 15% every
OL,9,FFriday and Saturday at Sainsbury's and
OL,10,Fon pay day at Argos.
OL,12,FPrerana Issar, the chief people
OL,13,Fofficer at Sainsbury's, said: "As the
OL,14,Ffestive season draws near, we're
OL,15,Fgetting ready to create a memorable
OL,16,FChristmas for our customers ` and our
OL,17,Fbrilliant colleagues play a central
OL,18,Frole in bringing this to life.
