OL,6,F"Joining us during this busy time is a
OL,7,Ffantastic opportunity to meet great
OL,8,Fpeople and acquire skills that will
OL,9,Fstay with you long after the festive
OL,10,Fseason."
OL,12,FSainsbury's is the UK's second largest
OL,13,Fsupermarket, behind Tesco, with about
OL,14,F1,400 supermarkets and local shops
OL,15,Facross the country.
OL,17,FIt reported an increase in sales last
OL,18,FChristmas, with customers buying
OL,19,Frecord numbers of pigs in blankets,
OL,20,Fmince pies and sparkling wine.
